h name\n|ko=얼음귀신 \'\'Urumkisin\'\'|komeaning=From {{tt|얼음 \'\'eol\'eum\'\'|ice}} and {{tt|귀신 \'\'gwishin\'\'|ghost}}; literally \'\'"ice ghost"\'\'\n|zh_cmn=冰鬼護 \'\'Bīng Guǐ Hù\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=The characters {{tt|冰|ice}} and {{tt|鬼|ghost}} comes from its Japanese name. {{tt|護|to protect}} may refer to its shape as an ice hockey mask.\n|hi=ग्लेली \'\'Glalie\'\'|himeaning=Transliteration of English name\n}}\n<br clear="left">\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Ash\'s Glalie]]\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Ice}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Ice|prevnum=361|prev=Snorunt|nextnum=363|next=Spheal}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Firnontor]]\n[[es:Glalie]]\n[[fr:Oniglali]]\n[[it:Glalie]]\n[[ja:オニゴーリ]]\n[[zh:冰鬼护]]'}